channel.title: [TOOL] Code Generator 1.0 [TOOL]
channel.description:
A project that is not java related but will help in java alot. Server Code Generator 1.0 now you may have seen 0.5 or 0.7 but this is nothing like it. This release will proberly help 50% of you out there who cant be bothered to learn java or code in it and just like copy + pasting :D. This Release will hope following continue the following before it is released. We hope if you support us that you comment on its thread when it is released. Thanks now lets begin. [Permission to post at the end of my Post].
Features:- [Green = 100%, Yellow = 99%-1%, Red = 0%/Not Started] [color=yellow]- 508 Compability - 35% + Teleporting - 70% + Add Items - 100% + Shops - 0% + Autorespawn - 100% + NPC Drops - 40% + Other Commands [10] - 0% - 525 Compability - 0% + PK Gear - 0% + Teleporting - 0% + Add Items - 0% + Shops - 0% + Autospawn - 0% + NPC Drops - 0% + Other Commands [10] - 0% - 317 Coding [Silab Base] - 100% + Teleporting - 100% + Add Items - 100% + Set Skills - 100% + NPC Drops - 100% + Autospawn - 100% + Other Commands [15] - 100% - 377 Coding [Delta ect.] - 100% + Autospawning - 100% + NPC Drops 100% + Shops - 100% + Teleporting - 100% + Add Items - 100% + Other Commands [10] - 100% - 513 Coding [ScapeRune ect.] - 0% + Teleporting - 0% + Add Items - 0% + Shops - 0% + Autospawn - 0% + NPC Drops - 0% + Other Commands [10] - 0%
Pictures of finished Parts e.g 317:- [More Pics Added as I Progress] [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/95rguv.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i47.tinypic.com/23uu9ax.jpg[/img]
Some bits of the Source Code:- :D [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/16hlt78.jpg[/img] (FULL SIZE @ [url=http://i50.tinypic.com/16hlt78.jpg]http://i50.tinypic.com/16hlt78.jpg[/url])
The Project will be way better than it looks like and so far I've gotta 0.3% Of it Done. Giving me templates for codes will get you some credits! Mhmm Credits & Maybe some Cookies If im nice. This version may rack upto 500kb in size since 0.7 was around 300kb, The sizes are incredibily low for what they can produce. I cutted out alot wasteful codes to make it as small as possible. This Project will not END HERE. It will go on to proberly v3 which will proberly have coding for 600's if they are released at the time of its coding Lol! I repeat this is coded in VB 2008 if you require help on it please message me. If you support this please say so lol.
Permission to post:- [IMG]http://i47.tinypic.com/13yidro.jpg[/img] You get cookies :P
Note:- For complete retards this is my work not Miss Silabsoft's... If you want give her a link to here and she will check...
